From b5b02e86486916b67142096551f1ef92d04cdd3f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ripan Deuri <quic_rdeuri@quicinc.com>
Date: Mon, 24 Mar 2025 22:27:27 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 7/8] wifi: ath12k: Refactor data path pdev struct

Refactor struct ath12k_pdev_dp to encapsulate all DP related fields of
radio (ar) and rely on this single pdev object in per packet DP
operations to optimize cache usage.

Introduce an array of RCU-protected ath12k_pdev_dp in DP device object
to find DP pdev directly from the DP device object. Updates to this array
are protected by the dp_lock spinlock.

Signed-off-by: Ripan Deuri <quic_rdeuri@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <quic_hbijlani@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Aman Mehta <quic_amanmeht@quicinc.com>
